      "text": "Super Ōzumō: Netsusen Daiichiban (スーパー大相撲 熱戦大一番; \"Super Sumo of the Most Heated Competition\") is a sumo video game developed and published by Namcot for the Super Famicom, which was released exclusively in Japan on December 18, 1992.\nFamitsu gave it 26/40.",
